caption:
💡Did you know? Our Higher Standard Cream Blushes come in two gorgeous finishes — Satin Matte and Cream Glow! Same pigment-packed, skin-loving goodness… just with a lil’ twist ✨⁠
⁠
💖 Satin Matte: Ideal for oily/combo skin, this beauty sets itself, absorbs excess oil, and leaves a soft, natural finish. No extra steps needed.⁠
⁠
💫 Cream Glow: Perfect for dry to normal skin. Gives that radiant, dewy look we love 😍 You can set it with powder—but only if you want to.⁠
⁠
Both are beginner-friendly, blend like a dream, and come with a whole lotta love 💕 Which one’s calling your name?⁠
